  <name>Thunar</name>
  <summary>Modern, fast and easy-to-use file manager for Xfce</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Thunar is a file browser specifically designed for the Xfce Desktop, but also can
      serve as an alternate file browser for other Desktop environments. It has been
      designed from the ground up to be fast and easy-to-use.
    </p>
    <p>
      Its user interface is clean and intuitive, and does not include any confusing or
      useless options by default.
    </p>
  </description>

